\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 STEP 2
\f1\b0\fs27 When the dough is ready, tip it onto a lightly floured surface and divide into four. Roll into balls and leave to rest, covered with a tea towel or cling film for another hour.\cb1 \uc0\u8232 
\fs36 \
\ls1\ilvl0
