\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 STEP 4
\f1\b0\fs27 To make the pizza, heat a grill to its highest setting and get a heavy\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/content/top-five-non-stick-frying-pans"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 frying pan}}. On a floured surface push and stretch one of the balls of dough out into a circle roughly the same size as the frying pan. Slip the round onto a floured baking sheet and top with a quarter of the sauce, a scattering of cheese, a few basil leaves and a quarter of the mozzarella.\cb1 \uc0\u8232 
\fs36 \
\ls1\ilvl0
